title: About
text: We are committed to democratizing AI/ML knowledge by offering accessible resources that enable the implementation of lightweight models on consumer-grade hardware. Our goal is to empower individuals and communities, regardless of their tehcnical background to learn and confidently apply AI/ML in their domain.
